"Haven't had a fight like that in years. It's good to be reminded of what it means to drop the pretensions and hold a weapon."</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"Commander Clyver said you're working with an animancer to build forge knights."</DefaultText><FemaleText>"Commander Clyver said you're working with an animancer to build forge knights."</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"اینجا چه کار می‌کنی؟"</DefaultText><FemaleText>"اینجا چه کار می‌کنی؟"</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"خداحافظ."</DefaultText><FemaleText>"خداحافظ."</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>Dunstan massages his temples, leaving soot streaks on the sides of his face. "So much for his talk of secrecy. Aye, I'm building Clyver's metal warriors. He says they're what we need to keep order in Defiance Bay, so..." He shrugs and shakes his head.</DefaultText><FemaleText>Dunstan massages his temples, leaving soot streaks on the sides of his face. "So much for his talk of secrecy. Aye, I'm building Clyver's metal warriors. He says they're what we need to keep order in Defiance Bay, so..." He shrugs and shakes his head.</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"How are you creating these forge knights?"</DefaultText><FemaleText>"How are you creating these forge knights?"</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"And you need Vianna's research to complete them."</DefaultText><FemaleText>"And you need Vianna's research to complete them."</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>[Give him Vianna's research.] "I think this is what you've been looking for."</DefaultText><FemaleText>[Give him Vianna's research.] "I think this is what you've been looking for."</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>[Show him the pieces of the Blade of the Endless Paths.] "I found several fragments of an ancient sword. Do you think you could repair it?"</DefaultText><FemaleText>[Show him the pieces of the Blade of the Endless Paths.] "I found several fragments of an ancient sword. Do you think you could repair it?"</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>Dunstan gives a low whistle. "That's a fine blade, indeed." He holds one fragment in his rough hands. "Looks Aedyran. Special-made. Must've been a commission for a champion of some sort."</DefaultText><FemaleText>Dunstan gives a low whistle. "That's a fine blade, indeed." He holds one fragment in his rough hands. "Looks Aedyran. Special-made. Must've been a commission for a champion of some sort."</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>[Show him the pieces of the Blade of the Endless Paths.] "I've found all of the pieces of this ancient sword. Do you think you could repair it?"</DefaultText><FemaleText>[Show him the pieces of the Blade of the Endless Paths.] "I've found all of the pieces of this ancient sword. Do you think you could repair it?"</FemaleText></Entry><Entry ID=""><DefaultText>"Aye, and 'twould be a privilege to. Not often you get to lay eyes on such fine craftsmanship."

